node.text: Its Always Raining In Gainesville! Had a Shooting contest while waiting out a ⛈! Swipe to the right !

Introducing @theterpometer to the UK and Europe, the worlds first essential oil application tool 🤓🙌 This is probably the most useful product we have used in recent times 🏅

Allows you to throw away your timers and the guesswork allowing for perfect temperature dabs that only enail tech could offer.

The terpometres LCD shows the temperature of your banger in real time!! Weve been using the enail much less as these give an even more accurate reading to the actual surface temp your dabbing in rather than an algorithm using pre inputed data.

The other end features a dabber!

These retail for £119.99 shipped to your door 🙏

Pre orders will ship today and we have a few available which will be added to the website shortly.

Lots of new drops next week 😎 and also our 6k comp 🙌

Stay tuned.

As of midnight, it will be my birthday, and I will have made it a quarter century in this bizarre world we call earth. What a time to be alive.

I’ve decided to make a new tradition. Every year for now on, I’m going to do a giveaway on my birthday. And to start it off, I’ll be giving away these @trevymetal and @doshworld marbles.

To enter: all you gotta do is like this post, and leave a comment about something you’re thankful for.

I’ll start it off. I’m thankful for the beautiful friends I’ve made in the last 25 years that have become closer than family. You know who you are.

And that’s it! I’ll choose a winner sometime tomorrow(maybe/if I remember)
